00:34:25.200 --> 00:34:27.869
victim mentality.

00:34:31.720 --> 00:34:35.430
We brush

00:34:35.430 --> 00:34:35.440
ourselves

00:34:35.440 --> 00:34:37.389
up and we stand against the

00:34:37.399 --> 00:34:39.149
devil.

00:34:49.280 --> 00:34:52.909
Praise the Lord, ladies and

00:34:52.919 --> 00:34:54.909
gentlemen. I appreciate you joining me

00:34:54.919 --> 00:34:56.790
today. We prayed for Donald Trump's

00:34:56.800 --> 00:34:59.230
marriage and covering over his

00:34:59.240 --> 00:35:02.230
children.

00:35:17.920 --> 00:35:21.230
A thousand shall fall at

00:35:21.240 --> 00:35:24.550
our side and ten thousand at our right hand,

00:35:24.560 --> 00:35:27.910
but nothing shall come nigh us.

00:35:27.920 --> 00:35:30.550
That's a promise.

00:35:30.560 --> 00:35:33.310
Every

00:35:33.320 --> 00:35:35.190
tongue that rises against us, we

00:35:35.200 --> 00:35:37.950
condemn it.

00:35:41.560 --> 00:35:45.109
Like

00:35:45.119 --> 00:35:47.310
Pastor Billy said, whenever you

00:35:47.320 --> 00:35:49.230
see a bad commercial on TV

00:35:49.230 --> 00:35:49.240
that

00:35:49.240 --> 00:35:51.750
gives

00:35:51.750 --> 00:35:51.760
statistics

00:35:51.760 --> 00:35:54.630
about

00:35:54.640 --> 00:35:57.270
cancer, you speak out

00:35:57.280 --> 00:35:59.270
loud, 'No! That's not going to happen to

00:36:17.510 --> 00:36:17.520
me!'Don't

00:36:36.960 --> 00:36:39.150
let

00:36:39.160 --> 00:36:40.270
them bear

00:36:40.280 --> 00:36:44.030
fruit. I'm not a statistic.

00:37:12.280 --> 00:37:15.950
I'm not of this world! They always

00:37:15.960 --> 00:37:17.589
ask me at the doctor

00:37:17.599 --> 00:37:19.630
about

00:37:21.470 --> 00:37:21.480
family

00:37:23.349 --> 00:37:23.359
history.

00:37:24.640 --> 00:37:25.990
They're doing what they've been trained

00:37:26.000 --> 00:37:28.470
to do,

00:37:28.480 --> 00:37:29.870
but

00:37:38.720 --> 00:37:41.829
I'm not

00:37:41.839 --> 00:37:45.190
under the curse! Jesus has set me

00:37:45.200 --> 00:37:48.069
free.

00:38:04.960 --> 00:38:07.069
Heart disease?

00:38:07.079 --> 00:38:10.349
I'm not taking that.

00:38:13.400 --> 00:38:15.829
I have a new

00:38:15.839 --> 00:38:18.589
DNA inside of me;

00:38:18.599 --> 00:38:20.829
I have the blood of Jesus Christ that

00:38:20.839 --> 00:38:24.349
has set me free from generational

00:38:24.359 --> 00:38:26.829
curses.

00:38:38.839 --> 00:38:42.470
But you have to actively

00:38:42.480 --> 00:38:45.470
resist the

00:38:45.480 --> 00:38:48.349
devil. You have to fight him from a place

00:38:48.359 --> 00:38:51.470
of being full! Don't fight him from a

00:38:51.480 --> 00:38:54.990
place of empty,

00:38:57.560 --> 00:39:01.230
otherwise

00:39:05.640 --> 00:39:07.670
you're going to get

00:39:07.680 --> 00:39:09.950
your hiney whipped. Remember the seven sons

00:39:09.960 --> 00:39:11.710
of

00:39:15.030 --> 00:39:15.040
Sceva?

00:39:18.200 --> 00:39:20.510
They got their

00:39:20.520 --> 00:39:22.870
hinies whipped because they

00:39:22.880 --> 00:39:25.470
did not have the

00:39:25.480 --> 00:39:28.069
revelation of who He was.

00:40:34.920 --> 00:40:37.190
Does hell know your

00:40:37.200 --> 00:40:39.910
name? I have to

00:40:39.920 --> 00:40:42.109
ask you that today. Do they know who you

00:40:42.119 --> 00:40:43.950
are in the pits of

00:40:43.960 --> 00:40:47.190
hell?

00:40:51.599 --> 00:40:55.390
Fight from a place of full, not from

00:40:55.400 --> 00:40:57.710
a place of empty. Well, glory to God!

00:41:03.720 --> 00:41:06.390
Thank you for joining me today,

00:41:06.400 --> 00:41:08.510
y'all.

00:41:11.240 --> 00:41:12.790
We're making a difference.

00:41:24.040 --> 00:41:27.390
May His face

00:41:27.400 --> 00:41:28.550
shine on

00:41:28.560 --> 00:41:31.270
you

00:41:33.160 --> 00:41:35.950
and give you peace today.

00:41:57.960 --> 00:42:00.790
In

00:42:00.800 --> 00:42:02.270
this Christmas season, we say, 'Happy

00:42:02.280 --> 00:42:03.829
birthday, Jesus!'We sing 'Happy Birthday'to Him,

00:42:03.829 --> 00:42:03.839
or even that Stevie Wonder song:

00:42:03.839 --> 00:42:08.750
'Happy birthday to you.'Stevie

00:42:08.750 --> 00:42:08.760
Wonder's is a

00:42:08.760 --> 00:42:12.150
happy

00:42:30.190 --> 00:42:30.200
song—it's

00:42:45.359 --> 00:42:48.549
fun!

00:42:59.800 --> 00:43:03.390
We play it every year and say,

00:43:03.400 --> 00:43:05.829
'Jesus, it's your

00:43:07.520 --> 00:43:12.790
birthday!'Tomorrow

00:43:15.359 --> 00:43:17.790
I'll

00:43:17.800 --> 00:43:19.349
talk to you all more about the

00:43:19.359 --> 00:43:20.270
thousand-year

00:43:20.280 --> 00:43:23.870
reign

00:43:23.880 --> 00:43:28.150
and what we do after it.

00:43:45.680 --> 00:43:49.349
The Lord Jesus is coming and He has

00:43:49.359 --> 00:43:51.390
a mansion for you.

00:43:54.359 --> 00:43:57.510
He was showing me the

00:43:57.520 --> 00:44:02.230
depth of the martyr's

00:44:02.240 --> 00:44:04.790
crown

00:44:07.440 --> 00:44:09.589
and

00:44:12.960 --> 00:44:16.230
how much of an

00:44:16.240 --> 00:44:21.870
honor it is in heaven. He showed me

00:44:21.880 --> 00:44:22.910
a

00:44:22.920 --> 00:44:25.349
man who sowed in

00:44:25.359 --> 00:44:27.589
secret a

00:44:27.599 --> 00:44:29.549
lot—he

00:44:29.559 --> 00:44:32.230
gave

00:44:32.240 --> 00:44:34.870
away

00:44:34.880 --> 00:44:39.750
over $53 million

00:44:42.720 --> 00:44:45.589
but

00:44:45.599 --> 00:44:47.069
never

00:44:47.079 --> 00:44:51.109
once wanted recognition.

00:45:23.520 --> 00:45:25.510
The Lord showed

00:45:25.520 --> 00:45:28.790
me

00:45:28.800 --> 00:45:33.349
his robe in heaven, breathtaking

00:45:33.349 --> 00:45:33.359
with

00:45:33.359 --> 00:45:35.349
gold

00:45:39.839 --> 00:45:42.470
designs.

00:46:01.880 --> 00:46:04.470
If you get praise for it on this side,

00:46:04.480 --> 00:46:06.230
there's no blessing like that on

00:46:06.240 --> 00:46:07.150
the other side.

00:46:52.559 --> 00:46:54.349
You're going to be

00:46:54.359 --> 00:46:57.109
amazed that it's the little granny

00:46:57.119 --> 00:46:59.030
in the corner who gave her widow's mite,

00:46:59.030 --> 00:46:59.040
who interceded

00:46:59.040 --> 00:47:02.549
for the preacher.

00:47:21.839 --> 00:47:23.430
The last will be first and the first

00:47:23.440 --> 00:47:24.870
will be

00:47:24.880 --> 00:47:27.589
last. If you want

00:47:27.599 --> 00:47:30.630
to hear God the most, go clean a

00:47:30.640 --> 00:47:33.230
toilet!

00:47:35.240 --> 00:47:37.309
There's

00:47:37.319 --> 00:47:40.150
something beautiful in it.

00:48:02.480 --> 00:48:03.950
I did

00:48:21.150 --> 00:48:21.160
that

00:48:41.960 --> 00:48:43.589
for

00:49:04.520 --> 00:49:07.190
15

00:49:09.390 --> 00:49:09.400
years—some

00:49:12.839 --> 00:49:14.870
of the nastiest things

00:49:14.880 --> 00:49:18.510
you'll ever see, like cleaning up diarrhea when people would mess themselves. But

00:49:33.760 --> 00:49:36.030
I learned how to

00:49:36.040 --> 00:49:39.069
truly worship

00:49:39.079 --> 00:49:43.910
Him in those hard

00:49:43.920 --> 00:49:51.150
times. He became

00:49:51.160 --> 00:49:53.030
real.

00:50:17.280 --> 00:50:19.710
Well, I pray this video blessed you

00:50:20.950 --> 00:50:20.960
and

00:50:23.920 --> 00:50:27.230
put a

00:50:27.240 --> 00:50:30.109
smile on your face.

00:50:30.119 --> 00:50:32.710
Jesus loves you so much,

00:50:32.720 --> 00:50:35.470
and we will see you all again

00:50:35.480 --> 00:50:38.470
tomorrow.

00:50:38.480 --> 00:50:41.630
Praise the Lord, y'all have a great

00:50:41.640 --> 00:50:44.920
night. Bye-bye.

